Global Meta Tag Editor: Control the SEO title/desc of every page from one view.
Sitemap.xml Generator: Auto-rebuild sitemap when new blogs are added.
Canonical Link Manager: Prevent duplicate content issues.
Redirect Manager (301/302): Map old URLs to new ones without editing .htaccess.
Structured Data (Schema) Builder: Inject JSON-LD for "Products" and "FAQ" automatically.
OpenGraph Previewer: See how your site looks on Facebook/WhatsApp before publishing.
Keyword Density Checker: Analysis Tool for blog content.
Robots.txt Editor: Control search engine crawling from the UI.
Google Analytics/GTM Integration: Input fields for tracking IDs.
Pixel Tracking Manager: Inject Facebook/TikTok pixel code snippets.
Internal Tooling & Optimization
Asset Browser: A file manager for all images/PDFs uploaded to the site.
Global Text Search-and-Replace: Change "24/7" to "Mon-Fri" across all textual content in the DB.
Image Alt-Tag Batch Editor: Quickly add alt text to images that are missing it.
Cache Purge Button: Clear the Next.js cache/CDN with one click.
Database Health Check: Identify and remove orphaned blog categories or tags.
Error Log Viewer: Real-time view of server-side errors (Next.js logs).
Font Manager: Upload and swap system fonts for the frontend.
Color Palette Picker: Change the --accent and --surface variables globally.
Draft Preview Mode: A hidden link to view the site as it would look with current draft changes.
System Info Panel: Display Node.js version, allocated memory, and disk usage.
